t: Ona cestovat ziaden scribe bol available puto posta zaruka repayment! Jeden trusted v this chovanie he spatny listok puto when due he observe GOD jeho Lord Nie withhold any testimony by zatajit co ona svedok! Ktokolvek withholds testimony bol sinful o srdce GOD JE fully aware z everything ONA ROBIT